Syntax transformer-takes syntax and returns syntax
Define-syntax- making "transformer binding": replace syntax by output search-and-replace
Syntax-source stx, syntax-line stx, syntax-column stx-functions that access the syntax object
Syntax-datum-> converts it completely into an S-expression
cdr-returns second element of the pair p
Normal Racket code runs at run time
Syntax transformer-evaluates at compile time
Syntax transformer can rearrange the syntax: rewrite the code at compile time. The pieces of syntax are moved around, but they aren't actually evaluated until run time.
